it";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:361:"WooCommerce Multilingual 3.8.2 &#8211; keeping up with WooCommerce and continuing compatibility with other extensions. And other fixes. WooCommerce 2.6 was released not long ago and we made sure that our plugin will accommodate all new changes in our previous versions. Yet a couple of things slipped through and we addressed them in this new release. [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5:"Mihai";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4350:"<p><strong>WooCommerce Multilingual 3.8.2 &#8211; keeping up with WooCommerce and continuing compatibility with other extensions. And other fixes.</strong></p>\n<p>WooCommerce 2.6 was released not long ago and we made sure that our plugin will accommodate all new changes in our previous versions. Yet a couple of things slipped through and we addressed them in this new release.</p>\n<p>Some of these changes impacted different WooCommerce extensions or how our WooCommerce Multilingual works together with them. These issues were also addressed in version 3.8.2<br />\nHere are some extensions for which we fixed compatibility problems in the new version (not all are directly related to WooCommerce 2.6) :</p>\n<ul>\n<li>WooCommerce Table Rate Shipping: new logic for shipping classes required some logic to be updated in this extension but also on the compatibility logic from our end.</li>\n<li>Dynamic Pricing: the discount was not shown on the mini-cart</li>\n<li>Product Add-ons: some strings were not translated</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We also added a new filter (&#8216;wcml_product_custom_prices&#8217;) that allows other plugins to programmatically adjust or simply set custom prices for products.</p>\n<p>The translatable fields for external products are not placed into a separate section in the products translation editor. Previously they were simply listed as custom fields.</p>\n<p><a href="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/2016-07-12_1149.png"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-953474" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/2016-07-12_1149.png" alt="external products" width="600" height="234" srcset="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/2016-07-12_1149.png 1030w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/2016-07-12_1149-150x59.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/2016-07-12_1149-300x117.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/2016-07-12_1149-768x300.png 768w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/2016-07-12_1149-1024x400.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></a></p>\n<p>You can find the list of all the changes that are more significant in the <a href="https://wpml.org/download/woocommerce-multilingual/?section=changelog">changelog</a>.</p>\n<p>Last but not the least important, WooCommerce Multilingual 3.8.2 is faster. Larger changes in version 3.8 and fine-tuning done in the following versions allow sites (especially larger sites) to have load times even with 20-25% smaller on shop related pages from the front end. The effort for improving these numbers even further continues and it&#8217;s also combined with current work being done in WPML.</p>\n<h2>Getting the update</h2>\n<p>You should receive this update automatically to the WordPress admin. If you want, you can also download WooCommerce Multlingual from the <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/woocommerce-multilingual/">WordPress downloads page</a>.</p>\n<p>Speaking of wordpress.org, if you think that our plugin makes your life easier and better, please <strong><a href="https://wordpress.org/support/view/plugin-reviews/woocommerce-multilingual?rate=5#postform">rate WooCommerce Multilingual</a></strong> to let others know that they could experience the same thing. Thanks in advance!</p>\n<h2>Need technical help?</h2>\n<p>If you need help with WooCommerce Multilingual, please start a new thread in <a href="https://wpml.org/forums/forum/english-support/">WPML support</a>. Then, add a comment here with a brief description and a link to that thread. We&#8217;ll follow up and make sure that everything gets handled.</p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=IwAkTnRKs-M:ehhNfdzS8eI:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=IwAkTnRKs-M:ehhNfdzS8eI:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=IwAkTnRKs-M:ehhNfdzS8eI:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=IwAkTnRKs-M:ehhNfdzS8eI:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=IwAkTnRKs-M:ehhNfdzS8eI:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=IwAkTnRKs-M:ehhNfdzS8eI:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/IwAkTnRKs-M" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:61:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/woocommerce-multilingual-3-8-2/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"4";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:56:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/woocommerce-multilingual-3-8-2/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:4;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:42:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:61:"WPML and Capita integrate through SmartMATE WordPress Connect";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/4_ZJ-rfxa-M/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:84:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/wpml-capita-integrates-smartmate-wordpress-connect/#respond";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Thu, 07 Jul 2016 20:02:48 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Announcements";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:26:"https://wpml.org/?p=948097";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:404:"Today we are happy to announce and present SmartMATE WordPress Connect, the recent integration between WPML and Capita, a leading translation service. Capita Translation and Interpreting (Capita TI) is a leading provider of language services to both public and private organisations. They offer a wide range of professional translation and interpreting services, including website localisation, [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Ornela Flores";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:3003:"<p>Today we are happy to announce and present SmartMATE WordPress Connect, the recent integration between <a href="https://wpml.org">WPML</a> and <a href="http://www.capitatranslationinterpreting.com/">Capita</a>, a leading translation service.</p>\n<p><img class="size-medium wp-image-948139 aligncenter" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlCapita-1-300x118.png" alt="wpml+Capita" width="300" height="118" srcset="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlCapita-1-300x118.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlCapita-1-150x59.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/wpmlCapita-1.png 347w" sizes="(max-width: 300px) 100vw, 300px" /></p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Capita Translation and Interpreting (Capita TI) is a leading provider of language services to both public and private organisations. They offer a wide range of professional translation and interpreting services, including website localisation, face-to-face interpreting, voiceover and subtitling, and multilingual SEO, in over 180 languages.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">They can offer extensive experience and resources, as well as reliable end-to-end solutions to help businesses and community groups translate everything, from websites and important documentation, to software and digital files, so that internal stakeholders and customers alike can understand the information they require, no matter what language they speak.</p>\n<p style="text-align: left;">Their  processes and capabilities are demonstrated by their ISO accreditations in information security; quality of management systems; and environmental management.</p>\n<p>Now, with SmartMATE WordPress Connect you will enjoy:</p>\n<p>·        Seamless system integration</p>\n<p>·        Quick and secure set-up process</p>\n<p>·        Eliminate manual copy/paste tasks</p>\n<p>·        Full user control and visibility over translation projects</p>\n<p>·        Cost and time savings achieved through Capita&#8217;s innovative Language Technology</p>\n<p>To learn more about the new SmartMATE WordPress Connect, please visit: <a href="https://wpml.org/translation-service/capita/">https://wpml.org/translation-service/capita/</a></p>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=4_ZJ-rfxa-M:qusn5Xxpiv0:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/wpml/~4/4_ZJ-rfxa-M" height="1" width="1" alt=""/>";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:81:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/wpml-capita-integrates-smartmate-wordpress-connect/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:42:"http://rssnamespace.org/feedburner/ext/1.0";a:1:{s:8:"origLink";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:76:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/wpml-capita-integrates-smartmate-wordpress-connect/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:45:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:6:{s:0:"";a:7:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Compatible Plugins – Jul 2016";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/wpml/~3/Yq5gT5_tJ5Q/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:62:"https://wpml.org/2016/07/compatible-plugins-jul-2016/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Tue, 05 Jul 2016 11:28:16 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Announcements";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:13:"Compatibility";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:26:"https://wpml.org/?p=941331";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:347:"Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible plugins. The plugins are, XML Sitemap &#38; Google News feeds ,PiwigoPress, VR Calendar Pro, Buttons Shortcode and Widget, WP All Export, Super Store Finder, Widgetize Pages Light. If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view [&#8230;]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:15:"Mohamed Khafaja";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:5727:"<p><img class="aligncenter wp-image-941424" src="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Compatible-Plugins-Header-300x90.png" alt="Compatible Plugins-Header" width="400" height="121" srcset="https://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Compatible-Plugins-Header-300x90.png 300w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Compatible-Plugins-Header-150x45.png 150w, https://wpml.org/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/Compatible-Plugins-Header.png 680w" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" /></p>\n<p>Today we are happy to announce a few WPML compatible plugins.</p>\n<p>The plugins are, <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/xml-sitemap-feed/">XML Sitemap &amp; Google News feed</a>s ,<a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/piwigopress/">PiwigoPress</a>, <a href="https://codecanyon.net/item/vr-calendar-sync-pro-responsive-booking-plugin/13504469">VR Calendar Pro</a>, <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/buttons-shortcode-and-widget/">Buttons Shortcode and Widget</a>, <a href="http://www.wpallimport.com/export/">WP All Export</a>, <a href="https://codecanyon.net/item/super-store-finder-for-wordpress/11334595">Super Store Finder</a>, <a href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/widgetize-pages-light/">Widgetize Pages Light</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you’re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, we welcome you and ready to help: You are welcome to contact us at <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>.</p>\n<p>In order to expedite the process, we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a href="https://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a>. It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin Multilingual Ready.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">XML Sitemap &amp; Google News feeds</h2>\n<blockquote><p>This plugin dynamically creates feeds that comply with the XML Sitemap and the Google News Sitemap protocol.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/xml-sitemap-feed/">Download XML Sitemap &amp; Google News feeds<br />\n</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">PiwigoPress</h2>\n<blockquote><p>From any open API Piwigo gallery, swiftly include your photos in Posts/Pages and/or add randomized thumbnails and menus in your sidebar.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/piwigopress/">Download PiwigoPress</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">VR Calendar Sync Pro</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/vr-calendar-sync-pro-responsive-booking-plugin/13504469">Purchase VR Calendar Sync Pro</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Buttons Shortcode and Widget</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Create buttons. Nice and easy interface. Insert anywhere in your site &#8211; page/post editor, sidebars, template files.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/buttons-shortcode-and-widget/">Download Buttons Shortcode and Widget</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">WP All Export</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Customize the layout of the export file. Edit your data and re-import it later with WP All Import.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://www.wpallimport.com/export/">Purchase WP All Export</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Super Store Finder</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Super Store Finder for WordPress is a fully-featured WordPress Plugin integrated with Google Maps API v3 that allows customers to locate your stores easily.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://codecanyon.net/item/super-store-finder-for-wordpress/11334595">Purchase Super Store Finder</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Widgetize Pages Light</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Drop widgets in page or post content area. Widgetized pages. Build your custom Responsive page layout in no time.</p></blockquote>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://wordpress.org/plugins/widgetize-pages-light/">Download Widgetize Pages Light</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feedflare">\n<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:D7DqB2pKExk"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:D7DqB2pKExk" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:gIN9vFwOqvQ"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:gIN9vFwOqvQ" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?a=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:V_sGLiPBpWU"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/wpml?i=Yq5gT5_tJ5Q:XuDaUfwf-oY:V_sGLiPBpWU" border="0"></img></a>\n</div><img src="http://feeds.feedbu